tio between bulge and disk stars, and the theoretical yields by massive stars\nagree with the observed ratios, leaving no space for AGB contribution to Al.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Oct 2006 00:46:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
